*Misli* da će lako doći do cilja. (He thinks he will easily reach the goal.)

*Mislila* sam da ću naći nešto zanimljivo. (I thought I would find something interesting.)

*Misle* da je ona dobra sportistkinja. (They think she is a good athlete.)

*Mislio* je da je spreman za ispit. (He thought he was ready for the exam.)

*Misliti* ću o tome kako da rešim problem. (I will think about how to solve the problem.)